item.title: A Kodi build for the lands down under

NOTE: If you get a {Backup Error} you will need to click [OK] twice on settings. Then go down to {Addons} and click [OK]. Then click [OK] on {My Addons} and go down to {Program Addons} and click [OK]. Now go down to {Backup} and click [OK]. Now scroll to {Update} and click [OK]. Update the addon to version {1.1.0} and click [BACK] until you are at the start. Now restart the aNZac Update process and click [OK] on {Restore}.
